questions: What is the description of the observation with the code {observation_code}?
sparql: PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX syn: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX loinc: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#loinc:LOINC> SELECT DISTINCT ?description WHERE {{ ?observation a syn:Observation; syn:code '{observation_code}'^^loinc:; syn:description ?description. }}
